node.text: When we take care of people, we take care of the planet. We’re donating 100M disease-resistant coffee trees by 2025 to help farmers and their communities, and committing to reduce our landfill waste by 50% by 2030.

node.title: Caring for Our Planet & Our People

node.text: Why is Nitro Cold Brew so whoa? Bill Nye explains.

node.title: Bill Nye Presents Nitro Cold Brew

node.accessibility_caption: Hand holds a Pink Drink above the clear blue waters of a swimming pool.

A Dragon Drink sits on an outdoor surface in front of a pink wall that matches the drink’s color. The shadows of two hands doing peace signs can be seen on the wall, and two palm trees rise up behind the wall as well.
Two hands hold up a Pink Drink and a Strawberry Acai Starbucks Refreshers drink in front of a tree of green leaves.

node.text:
Strawberry summer duo. 💕
🍓 Pink Drink
🍓 Strawberry Acai Starbucks Refreshers® drink

node.accessibility_caption: Tweet from Starbucks on a mint green background that says, "In-person coffee dates. 💚"
An Iced Matcha Tea Latte sits on an outdoor countertop, and is surrounded by dreamy light refractions that cover the scene.

node.text: Summer’s perfect matcha. 🌴  Iced Matcha Tea Latte

node.accessibility_caption: A hand holds up an Iced Passion Tango Tea in front of a mural of vibrant, multi-colored leaves.
A hand holds up a Caramel Ribbon Crunch Frappuccino Drink in front of an outdoor mural, painted with ribbons of orange, sky blue, and cream.

node.text: Caramel mmmood. 😋 Caramel Ribbon Crunch Frappuccino® Drink

node.accessibility_caption: A Starbucks Nitro Cold Brew sits on a table on an urban balcony, overlooking the tops of buildings. A few plants on the balcony fill out the scene for a comforting, sunny day.
Hand holds up a hot Starbucks cup in front of a bush blooming with white and yellow flowers.

node.text: Raise your hand if you're still drinking hot coffee in the summer. ✋☕ 📷: @seeyaaali

node.accessibility_caption: Two hands each hold up a Strawberry Funnel Cake Frappuccino Drink in front of a car’s open sunroof, which shows a bright blue sky.

node.text: Road trippin’, summer sippin’. 🚗 Strawberry Funnel Cake Frappuccino® Drink
